text: Magdiel Estrada (born August 26, 1994) is a Cuban judoka. He competed at the 2016 Summer Olympics in the men's 73 kg event, in which he was eliminated in the second round by Lasha Shavdatuashvili. ==References== Category:1994 births Category:Living people Category:Cuban male judoka Category:Olympic judoka of Cuba Category:Judoka at the 2016 Summer Olympics Category:Pan American Games medalists in judo Category:Pan American Games gold medalists for Cuba Category:Judoka at the 2015 Pan American Games Category:Judoka at the 2019 Pan American Games
title: Magdiel Estrada
